						               													<description>Les Gens Qui is THE party game to judge all the people who annoy us every day. It's a simple, fast and interactive card game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The aim of the game? Try to guess what your friends think of these people.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player chooses a set of hand cards which will allow them to choose from 4 different sanctions: Heart On You, Just a Finger , One Year of Gulag or Death Sentence.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;One the players is the judge. He takes 3 situation cards, reads them at loud and puts them face up in the middle of the board.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;For example : &amp;#10;&amp;#10;     People who sniff instead of blowing their nose, &amp;#10;     People who say &amp;quot;I'm not a racist, but...&amp;quot;, &amp;#10;     People who are ALWAYS late.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The judge gives his opinion by placing cards face down on the board. The other players do the same and vote, face down, trying to guess what the Judge has voted. The player who have the most answers in common with the Judge score 1 point for each correct answer!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
